title: The Bedroom Three-way
description: College pals Corey, Tyler and Caitlyn are moving into a new apartment in the coming school year with three bedrooms: two small, one gloriously spacious. Who deserves the biggest room?
author: shows@maximumfun.org (Jesse Thorn)
